{
  "stem": "18102.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes I do, because it was a-- a big moment in my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had spent my seven odd years of life in one place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly, my father had decided that our bungalow, where we lived, was going to be unsafe during the bombings that might occur, whereas the building he had inherited from his father, which was on the outskirts of Bialystok, not in the industrial center, was a brick building, two story affair, and would be safer for us during this coming period of uncertainty and bombings.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we suddenly moved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember that quite vividly, because now I was suddenly living in an entirely different environment and neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, it was-- it was hardly a neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a cemetery across the street that occupied most of my panorama that I was able to see as a child.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So yes, it was a big difference in my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't, my father left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What-- what had happened-- the story is this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was one of the few, maybe only-- I'm not sure if there was another Jewish council member of the city, council of Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my father was a very prominent person in the city affairs and had been elected to the city council.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And may be the only Jew that was elected to the city council.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm not sure about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But as a member of the city council, he was called to a emergency meeting with the mayor of the city of Bialystock before war broke-- before the actual war-- strike that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Before, actually, the Germans entered our city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "About a week before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After war broke out, but before the Germans came into our city.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
